HEADWORD: Blin
<hw>Blin</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>blinnen</ets>, AS. <ets>blinnan</ets>; pref. <ets>be-</ets> +
