==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: blin
<hw>blin</hw>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>blini</plw>,
<plw>bliny</plw> or <plw>blinis</plw>.</plu> <ety>[Russian.]</ety>
<def>a thin buckwheat pancake made with yeast and usually filled with
sour cream and folded over. See also <er>blini</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

